---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/global/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---
<PageLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | inspir"
  description="Privacy policy for inspir learning LTD. How we collect, use, and protect your personal data under UK GDPR."
>
  <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'Privacy Policy' }]} />

  <section class="py-20 bg-cream">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-dark mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500 mb-12 text-sm">Last updated: January 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-10">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-dark mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">Who we are</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">inspir learning LTD ("inspir", "we", "us") is a company registered in England and Wales. Our registered address is London SW9 0PP. We are the data controller for personal data collected through this website and our services.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">Contact us for data-related enquiries: <a href="mailto:hello@inspir.uk" class="text-purple font-semibold hover:underline">hello@inspir.uk</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-dark mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">What data we collect</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">We collect personal data in the following ways:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0">·</span><span><strong class="text-dark">Enquiry form submissions:</strong> Name, email address, store URL, platform type, order volume, and any information you include in your message.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0">·</span><span><strong class="text-dark">Email communications:</strong> Email address and any personal data you include in messages to us.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0">·</span><span><strong class="text-dark">Analytics:</strong> Anonymous usage data including pages visited, time on site, and referral source. We use privacy-respecting analytics that do not collect personally identifiable information without consent.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0">·</span><span><strong class="text-dark">Cookies:</strong> See our <a href="/cookies" class="text-purple hover:underline">Cookie Policy</a> for details.</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-dark mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">How we use your data</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0">·</span>Responding to your enquiry and discussing our services</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0">·</span>Delivering the services you have engaged us to provide</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0">·</span>Sending service-related communications (invoices, reports, updates)</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0">·</span>Improving our website and services based on anonymous analytics</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0">·</span>Complying with our legal obligations</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">We do not sell your personal data. We do not use it for advertising purposes.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-dark mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">Legal basis for processing</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0">·</span><span><strong class="text-dark">Legitimate interests:</strong> Processing enquiry submissions and responding to potential clients.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0">·</span><span><strong class="text-dark">Contract performance:</strong> Processing data necessary to deliver services to existing clients.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0">·</span><span><strong class="text-dark">Legal obligation:</strong> Retaining records as required by UK law.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0">·</span><span><strong class="text-dark">Consent:</strong> For any non-essential cookies or marketing communications where applicable.</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-dark mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">Data retention</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">We retain personal data only for as long as necessary:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0">·</span>Enquiry data: Up to 24 months if no contract is entered into</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0">·</span>Client data: Duration of the contract plus 7 years for financial records</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0">·</span>Analytics data: 13 months maximum</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-dark mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">Your rights under UK GDPR</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">You have the following rights regarding your personal data:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0">·</span><span><strong class="text-dark">Access:</strong> Request a copy of the personal data we hold about you.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0">·</span><span><strong class="text-dark">Rectification:</strong> Request correction of inaccurate or incomplete data.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0">·</span><span><strong class="text-dark">Erasure:</strong> Request deletion of your personal data (subject to legal obligations).</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0">·</span><span><strong class="text-dark">Portability:</strong> Receive your data in a structured, machine-readable format.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0">·</span><span><strong class="text-dark">Objection:</strong> Object to processing based on legitimate interests.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-purple mt-1 flex-shrink-0">·</span><span><strong class="text-dark">Restriction:</strong> Request that we restrict processing in certain circumstances.</span></li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">To exercise any of these rights, email <a href="mailto:hello@inspir.uk" class="text-purple font-semibold hover:underline">hello@inspir.uk</a>. We will respond within one month.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3">You also have the right to lodge a complaint with the Information Commissioner's Office (ICO) at <a href="https://ico.org.uk" class="text-purple hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ico.org.uk</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-dark mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">Data processors and transfers</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We use a small number of third-party processors to deliver our services. All processors are subject to data processing agreements and comply with UK GDPR. We do not transfer personal data outside the UK/EEA without appropriate safeguards in place.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-10">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-dark mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">Changes to this policy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We may update this policy from time to time. The date at the top of this page indicates when it was last updated. Material changes will be communicated to existing clients directly.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
